I"E¬<p>Add selectboxes to make your form more intuitive by providing users with a set of options to choose from. You can add simple selectboxes with a label, use icons only or icons with labels. Alternatively, you can use pill selectboxes if they go well with your design.</p>

<div class="example no_toc_section">
