      <span class="nt">&lt;span</span> <span class="na">class=</span><span class="s">"form-selectgroup-label"</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span>JavaScript<span class="nt">&lt;/span&gt;</span>
    <span class="nt">&lt;/label&gt;</span>
  <span class="nt">&lt;/div&gt;</span>
<span class="nt">&lt;/div&gt;</span></code></pre></figure>

</div>

<h2 id="advanced-selectboxes">Advanced selectboxes</h2>

<p>Use more advanced selectboxes to display the range of available options. You can choose selectboxes with radio buttons, if you want users to select only one option or with checkboxes, if they are allowed to choose multiple options.</p>

<div class="example no_toc_section">
